data.description: Welcome to 6514 Comanche Post, built in 2020. The home features a 20 foot entrance immersing the home with tons of natural light, arches that greet you into the ample living room that features high ceilings and a built in wet bar. Kitchen features Stainless Steel appliances, Eat-in Bar top, Built-in oven, 42in Shaker style cabinets. Coffered ceilings through out home, Primary suite features tray ceiling, recess lighting, on suite features dual vanities, jetted tube, walk-in shower. 2nd floors features an oversized loft leading into bedroom 2,3,& 4.
